{"tid":913120,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"社交焦慮症","createTime":"2018-11-23T07:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T04:48:46.000Z","uid":131622,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"20aea31c47333911e42f07677b81ed161dcfd43b","tid":913120,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"成日一見到人就好緊張好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點開口同人傾計<br />\n講親野都尷尷尬尬咁<br />\n好驚人地見到得我自己一個唔知點睇我<br />\n想識新朋友但又唔知點入手<br />\n一諗起要返學就好驚<br />\n有朋友有好有唔好<br />\n有朋友就要social覺得好攰<br />\n冇朋友就冇人搵我分組做project<br />\n覺得要經營人際社交好攰<br />\n有冇人明我講緊咩<br />\n每日返學都好焦慮唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170be8739330f68d6eb23b8f971909eef989aa33","tid":913120,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"personality a"},{"pid":"3fae3f9ff0e6861fe10b517636034afbd72aa0c7","tid":913120,"uid":131622,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"同其他人講我有呢啲煩惱<br />\n佢地覺得好小事冇理我<br />\n但係社交問題好困擾我<br />\n令我冇晒自信<br />\n成日都好焦慮好緊張<br />\n精神愈黎愈差<br />\n仲影響到學業<br />\n一個傾到心事既朋友都冇<br />\n有煩惱唔知同邊個講<br />\n唯有上黎連登呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16245462999999d3a1439bfebc47650522291034","tid":913120,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"170be8739330f68d6eb23b8f971909eef989aa33","tid":913120,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"personality a"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:36:21.000Z","msg":"咩意思？"},{"pid":"e7bda2ebfd9f08be2b5b87362970da915c433f34","tid":913120,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"我都係一樣"},{"pid":"3d677aea81310cdb3cf499ff01cf00acc0caba1d","tid":913120,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7bda2ebfd9f08be2b5b87362970da915c433f34","tid":913120